katha nayagan ( tamil : கதாநாயகன் , english katha - story , nayagan - hero ) is a 1988 indian tamil comedy film , directed by muktha srinivasan and produced by ramaswamy govind and muktha s. ravi . the film stars pandiarajan , s. v. sekhar , rekha and manorama in lead roles . the film had musical score by chandra bose.remake of malayalam film nadodikattu